What value is returned by the call `mystery("COMPUTER")`?

```java
public static String mystery(String word)
{
    String ans = "";
    for (int k = word.length(); k > 0; k -= 2)
    {
        ans += word.substring(k - 1, k);
    }
    return ans;
}
```
